\f3\b\fs32 \cf3 Example Use Cases
\f1\b0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs32 \cf3 A citizen uploads some new digital evidence related to a factual assertion which they have made in the context of a benefit application. This is then indexed, annotated with metadata describing its origin and the level of confidence associated with it. An event is then published providing notification that it is now available.
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 \

\f2\fs32 A citizen presents an overseas identity card at a NINO application identity check, an image of this is uploaded to DWP Evidence and the Agent views the product side by side from an exemplar as an aid to determining validity.
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 \

\f2\fs32 The Notifications service is used to send a letter to a citizen requiring clerical specialisation (i.e. it cannot with fidelity be regenerated from a template). Once it has generated the required content, it stores a PDF version of the letter in DWP Evidence, along with metadata describing its context, time and date of sending. An event is then published providing notification that this evidence item is now available.
